The natural numbers are arranged on a hexagonal grid in a spiral starting from 1 at the center. The number 2026 is in layer 26.

In this spiral, the sum of the 6 neighbors of a number n in layer l (for n ≥ 3) is 6n + 30.

For 2026, this gives 6 × 2026 + 30 = 12156 + 30 = 12186.

\boxed{12186}
